#: ../../G/generate.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../G/generate.rst:9
msgid ""
"To produce something according to an algorithm or program or set of rules, "
"or as a (possibly unintended) side effect of the execution of an algorithm "
"or program. The opposite of :ref:`parse`\\. This term retains its "
"mechanistic connotations (though often humorously) when used of human "
"behavior. \"The guy is rational most of the time, but mention nuclear energy"
" around him and he'll generate :ref:`infinite` flamage.\""
msgstr ""
"アルゴリズム、プログラム、あるいは一連の規則に従って、または(おそらく意図しない)アルゴリズムやプログラムの実行の副作用として、何かを生み出すこと。\\"
" :ref:`parse`\\ "
"の反対。この用語は、人間の行動について使われるとき、その機械論的な含意を(しばしばユーモラスに)保持する。「あいつは大半は理性的なんだが、原子力の話を持ち出すと\\"
" :ref:`infinite`\\ なフレームを生成するぞ。」"
